{
  "id": "guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale",
  "title": "Set the source locale manually",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"set-the-source-locale-manually\" translation-result=\"on\">手动设置源语言环境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale#set-the-source-locale-manually\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"set-the-source-locale-manually\">Set the source locale manually<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale#set-the-source-locale-manually\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<a id=\"set-source-manually\"></a>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 已经包含 <code>en-US</code> 语言环境数据。当你将 <code>--localize</code> 选项与 <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"> <code>ng build</code> </a> 一起使用时，Angular CLI 会自动包含语言环境数据并设置 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 的值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular already contains locale data for <code>en-US</code>.\nThe Angular CLI automatically includes the locale data and sets the <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> value when you use the <code>--localize</code> option with <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要将应用程序的源语言环境手动设置为自动值以外的其他语言环境，请完成以下操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To manually set the source locale of an application to one other than the automatic value, complete the following actions.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/master/packages/common/locales\" title=\"angular/packages/common/locales | angular/angular | GitHub\">Angular 存储库</a> 中的“语言-语言环境”组合中搜索 ID。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Search for the ID in the language-locale combination in <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/master/packages/common/locales\" title=\"angular/packages/common/locales | angular/angular | GitHub\">the Angular repository</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">设置 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"> <code>LOCALE_ID</code> </a> 令牌。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Set the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> token.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下示例将 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 的值设置为法语的 <code>fr</code> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example sets the value of <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> to <code>fr</code> for French.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"i18n/doc-files/app.module.ts\" header=\"src/app/app.module.ts\" region=\"locale-id\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a>, <a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a> } from '@angular/core';\nimport { <a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a> } from '@angular/platform-browser';\n\nimport { AppComponent } from '../src/app/app.component';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({\n  imports: [ <a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a> ],\n  declarations: [ AppComponent ],\n  providers: [ { provide: <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a>, useValue: 'fr' } ],\n  bootstrap: [ AppComponent ]\n})\nexport class AppModule { }\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 2021/9/15</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common\n - guide/i18n-optional\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\n - cli/build\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale#set-the-source-locale-manually\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/master/packages/common/locales\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"
}